# Maintenance and Cleanup Tools

The plugin includes tools for maintenance and cleanup of imported content.

## File Cleanup

File cleanup functionality:
- Implemented in [class-md-import-force-file-manager.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-file-manager.php)
- Removes old import files based on age
- Frontend interface in [cleanup.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/cleanup.js)

## Logging

The logging system:
- Logs errors and import activity to [logs/md-import-force.log](mdc:logs/md-import-force.log)
- Implementation in [class-md-import-force-logger.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-logger.php)
- Viewable through the Log tab in the admin interface

## Admin Interface

The maintenance interface is accessible through the Maintenance tab in [admin-page.php](mdc:templates/admin-page.php).
